Exactly 12 years ago today a little blue eyed girl entered this crazy world and became the glue that bound our family together. 

Being your mom has been one of the greatest joys of my life. There is absolutely nothing that you can not do. Your resilience and drive inspires me daily! I have loved showing you the world and I can’t wait for more travel and adventures together. Stay healthy, feisty, strong, fun and loving… Just the way you are, and I’ll be here always cheering you on! 

- xoxo Your Momster aka Mama 💋
